name: Experiment Or Die #28
description: Day 28 of a planned full year of collages, a new one every day using my years of photos and personal assets. Since I've been working on this collection every day I started to notice that if I took new photos and included them in my design that a time capsule of that day was created. Years from today I'll be able to look back at this design and it may trigger a recollection of exactly what I did on Sunday October 24, 2021. And I have hopes that something about this collection connects with you in a similar way. IG: Nikejerk.
